list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Initial commitAdd Choice class for contact management
This commit introduces the `Choice` class, which provides functionality for managing contacts. It includes options to add a new contact, edit an existing contact, and delete a contact. Each option is clearly documented within the code.
Improvements made in this commit: - Improved code formatting and alignment for better readability. - Added descriptive comments to explain the purpose of each code section. - Implemented a mechanism to avoid modifying the list while iterating through it during contact deletion.
This is the initial version of the `Choice` class, laying the foundation for contact management in our application.
